msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Third Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 22. Kalyāṇīsutta → janapadakalyāṇīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Kalyāṇīsutta "
msgstr "22. The Finest Lady in the Land "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn17.22:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.22:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … "
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.22:1.3"
msgid "na tassa, bhikkhave, janapadakalyāṇī ekā ekassa cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati yassa lābhasakkārasiloko cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr "Even if you’re alone with the finest lady in the land she might not occupy your mind, but possessions, honor and popularity would still occupy your mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.22:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … "
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …” "

msgctxt "sn17.22:1.5"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.22:1.6"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

